name: Bodycon Dress >Customizable Colors< ✧˖° (LoRA)
description:
Henlo ૮ • ﻌ - づ !! So this is a bit of an experiment for me but I think its good enough to post !! I made a clothing Lora !! Its a body con dress which has customizable colors !! this Lora shouldn't have too many issues as my last hopefully ! I hope you enjoy !! <3

I used ChillOutMix to train and produce some of the images !! Next time around ill try and use a more universal model ^^

This Lora works sorta well with anime models and semi realistic models !! so go wild with it !! ^^

I recommend keeping the weight at (1-0.7) and using the negative prompts as needed !! Higher weights tend to crop the image so I heavily recommend lower weights !!

weight values between 0.3 to 0.5 Seem to be more flexible especially for facial features and skin color !! So please lower weight if your having issues ^^

Important Trigger word Info (pls read)

I will be putting all the triggers words in a list so you choose the one you want easier ^^ !

  1. Long_Sleeve_Body_Con_Dress (is essential to getting the exact style of the images above)

  2. blue6722 (Gives you a basic Blue color)

  3. light_blue22222 (Gives you a lighter Blue color)

  4. army_green2244 (this one is self explanatory)

  5. pink5433 (Gives you a bright Barbie pink color)

  6. black0027 (Self explanatory)

  7. Marrón6666 (Gives you a dark orangish red color also)

If you add prompts like (huge breasts:1.2), Cleavage, Large breast and such you'll get a lower v neck for the dress ! ^^

Please also use these negative prompts (purse), (bag), (arm bag), ((cropped))

Some of the colors triggers don't work as well as the others !! just a heads up if your having issues getting the color you want !

So that's all the colors! I mainly put this here so there's no confusion (ෆ˙ᵕ˙ෆ)♡

>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>

Please use negative prompt Embedding (Easy Negative) it works a lot better with it then without it !! I've noticed many issues with odd hands as well so you can also use Bad-Hands-5 !!

I also highly recommend using the inpaint face trick to fix the faces !!

This Lora also works kind of well in combination with other Lora's ! you may have to lower the strength of my Lora if you wanna get the full likeness of the specific person !!

I had so much fun making the Lora and generating the images I hope you have as much fun as I did ⸜(｡˃ ᵕ ˂ )⸝♡ !!!

P.S If you've made it this far in the description, comment a link to a certain piece of clothing you'd like me to make a Lora of next ill definitely do it !! (๑ᵔ⤙ᵔ๑)

Please be kind with this Lora ♡

I recommend keeping the weight at (1-0.7) and using the negative prompts as needed !! Higher weights tend to crop the image so I heavily recommend lower weights !!

If you add prompts like (huge breasts:1.2), Cleavage, Large breast and such you'll get a lower v neck for the dress ! ^^

Here are all the settings used for most the examples:

Denoising strength: 0.45

Clip skip: 2

Hires upscale: 2

Hires upscaler: Latent (bicubic antialiased)

If you have any issues please tell me and ill try and help !! ૮₍ ˶ᵔ ᵕ ᵔ˶ ₎ა
